      "id": "PopularPost200690",
      "post_content": "@CrowJonSnow:  \n  \nYou said \"he had 3 creatures out, 2 of which were bears. i played this, tapped 1 for each bear, 3 for the other creature, and burned him for the rest\"  \n  \nI would like to know how you can send 3 damage to a third creature when fireball states: Fireball deals X damage EVENLY, rounded down, among any number of target creatures and/or players.  \n  \nSo in your scenario, by splitting the damage three ways, 1 damage to each bear, and 1 damage to the third creature would have been dealt by the wording of Fireball.",
      "posted_by": "Cqis",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost200690\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">@CrowJonSnow:<br/><br/>You said \"he had 3 creatures out, 2 of which were bears. i played this, tapped 1 for each bear, 3 for the other creature, and burned him for the rest\"<br/><br/>I would like to know how you can send 3 damage to a third creature when fireball states: Fireball deals X damage EVENLY, rounded down, among any number of target creatures and/or players.<br/><br/>So in your scenario, by splitting the damage three ways, 1 damage to each bear, and 1 damage to the third creature would have been dealt by the wording of Fireball.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '200690'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy72559\">Cqis</span>\r\n                                (9/27/2011 1:17:33 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=